1. *Baviš* se sportom već godinama. (You engage in sports for years.)
2. *Baviš* se odlično ovim zadatkom. (You're doing an excellent job with this task.)
3. Kako *baviš* svoje slobodno vreme? (How do you spend your free time?)
4. Ona se *bavi* pisanjem pesama. (She is involved in writing songs.)
5. Da li se *baviš* nekim hobijem? (Do you have a hobby?)
6. On se *bavi* izradom nameštaja. (He is engaged in furniture making.)
7. *Baviš* li se čitanjem knjiga? (Do you engage in reading books?)
8. Oni se *bave* istraživanjem novih tehnologija. (They are involved in researching new technologies.)
9. *Baviš* se ovom problematikom duže vreme? (Have you been dealing with this issue for a long time?)
10. Njegova firma se *bavi* proizvodnjom hrane. (His company is engaged in food production.)

Note: The word "baviš" is the second person singular present tense form of the verb "baviti se" which means "to engage in" or "to be involved in". The other forms of this verb used in the examples are: "baviš se" (reflexive form), "baviš", "bave se" (third person plural present tense), and "bave" (third person singular present tense).